{"4090260": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "救生員狂熱", "steam_appid": 4090260, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽故事簡介🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《NTR狂熱》(NTRaholic)精神續作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房東龍之介的堂哥「龍馬」，曾經是大學游泳隊的隊長，因為受傷而被迫中止運動員生涯。某天龍馬在一場賭局擊敗了當地企業家，贏得了一座游泳池的所有權，成為了一名「救生員」。在這座充滿著美女的游泳池，龍馬要一邊經營游泳池，一邊利用自己運動員的健壯身材與傲人體力，填滿清純害羞的女大生「水原蒼唯」等美女們寂寞的身與心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論她們有沒有男朋友，感情多麼堅定，做為一個傳奇的救生員，你必能將她們都搶奪過來！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/044e923cfe74ea668c67175f13aff375.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/044e923cfe74ea668c67175f13aff375.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/044e923cfe74ea668c67175f13aff375.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲內容🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家要扮演救生員、兼游泳池經營者龍馬，一邊壯大游泳池的生意，一邊享用游泳池的泳裝美女們。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天分為兩個時段，每個時段可以消耗行動值，進行不同的行動。可以專心經營游泳池，讓游泳池的生意變好，擊敗競爭對手；同時透過不同的小遊戲與女主角們更加親近，最後將他們徹底奪走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/4a850b4b3355208c5198fc7cc0011497.avif?t=1776758757\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras_big/4a850b4b3355208c5198fc7cc0011497.webp?t=1776758757 width=1560 height=877 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/f0a65a537b3255c95ef87a7201ea246c.avif?t=1776758757\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras_big/f0a65a537b3255c95ef87a7201ea246c.webp?t=1776758757 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&lt;游泳池經營&gt;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-管理泳池入場售票口，賺取收入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-派發傳單，增加游泳池的知名度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-修繕、升級游泳池不同區域的設施</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&lt;攻略女主角&gt;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-與她對話，推進劇情，享受她逐漸墮落的過程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-各種小遊戲，在公開課、私課撩撥她的情慾</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-在游泳池的不同角落，與她盡情交歡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/4ff7d4f229652623cde1a7af2694e471.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/4ff7d4f229652623cde1a7af2694e471.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/4ff7d4f229652623cde1a7af2694e471.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/dcd0588af1ad3f85338d4a26b583a231.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/dcd0588af1ad3f85338d4a26b583a231.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/dcd0588af1ad3f85338d4a26b583a231.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽遊戲玩法🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游泳池擁有不同的區域，其中各式設施都需要維護與升級，才能與競爭對手抗衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d9b690bbb8b36892d64e12983e4ac54e.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d9b690bbb8b36892d64e12983e4ac54e.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d9b690bbb8b36892d64e12983e4ac54e.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有穿著合適的游泳衣物，才能夠入場。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/3b713c2aad8775211893d35e9a2f733e.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/3b713c2aad8775211893d35e9a2f733e.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/3b713c2aad8775211893d35e9a2f733e.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在幫女主角「按摩」的時候，必須在她感覺不對勁的時候，趕緊將手抽開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d08a33bccd6b30cec893df1020ecb5a8.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d08a33bccd6b30cec893df1020ecb5a8.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d08a33bccd6b30cec893df1020ecb5a8.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性騷擾的過程如果被其他學員看到，警戒值就會提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/81ebe6783bbcdddaa3f3e22e7e816274.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/81ebe6783bbcdddaa3f3e22e7e816274.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/81ebe6783bbcdddaa3f3e22e7e816274.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d7cc75fb32aaea944fc5c3d266813dfb.poster.avif?t=1776758757\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d7cc75fb32aaea944fc5c3d266813dfb.webm?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4090260/extras/d7cc75fb32aaea944fc5c3d266813dfb.mp4?t=1776758757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔽角色介紹🔽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>水原 蒼唯</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >23歲，大學生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格內向，有一個溫柔的男朋友。<br>因為成長過程中曾受到欺負，最近才比較能夠表達自己的情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乍看之下是一個清純系的女友，但實際上男朋友不知道的是，她其實喜歡被拘束、粗暴的對待，渴望著各種硬核的Play。<br>而這些沒有被男友滿足，無處宣洩的性慾，帶著些許罪惡感，被她秘密寫在了日記當中…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>北川 美波</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >27歲，無職。目前借住在妹妹神楽的家裡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有個秘密的性癖